ALICIA:
What're you...?

40:47.610 --> 40:50.101
I thought your
plane was today.

40:50.140 --> 40:51.698
It was.
I'm late.

40:51.750 --> 40:53.001
Late?

40:53.050 --> 40:55.143
I think it-it's gone.

40:55.180 --> 40:58.889
I was reading Peter's
Gay/Straight Alliance speech,

40:58.920 --> 41:01.218
"The Double Danger
of Hate Crimes."

41:01.250 --> 41:04.253
It's pretty darn good.

41:04.290 --> 41:06.155
That's you, isn't it?

41:06.190 --> 41:07.851
You wrote that?

41:07.890 --> 41:09.221
No.

41:09.260 --> 41:13.526
Alicia, I can recognize
your cadence from a mile away.

41:13.570 --> 41:16.164
So you're Hillary?

41:16.200 --> 41:18.703
You're working your agenda
through him.

41:18.740 --> 41:21.163
We believe in the same
things, that's all.

41:26.810 --> 41:28.243
I'm sorry.

41:28.280 --> 41:30.077
For what?

41:30.120 --> 41:32.042
I wasn't here.

41:32.090 --> 41:34.240
You're in Oregon.

41:34.290 --> 41:36.986
I always thought of you
as the big sister.

41:37.020 --> 41:40.126
Well, I'm sorry that I wasn't
here when you needed me.

41:42.160 --> 41:43.957
I miss you.

41:44.000 --> 41:46.127
I know.

41:46.170 --> 41:48.730
No, you're supposed to say,
"I miss you, too."

41:48.770 --> 41:51.295
(laughing)

41:51.340 --> 41:53.535
I miss you, too.

41:53.570 --> 41:56.130
You don't need to be so strong.

41:58.110 --> 41:59.577
I'm not.

41:59.610 --> 42:02.010
I know.

42:02.050 --> 42:03.677
You don't need to pretend.

42:03.720 --> 42:06.018
Okay.

42:06.050 --> 42:07.586
(clears throat)

42:09.960 --> 42:11.279
(pats back)

42:21.200 --> 42:23.168
I like your apartment.

42:23.200 --> 42:25.168
Thanks.

42:30.610 --> 42:32.578
I'll phone.

42:32.610 --> 42:34.544
Okay.

42:40.920 --> 42:42.888
OWEN (outside):
I mean it.

42:42.920 --> 42:44.922
Okay.

